Beijing, February 11, 2020] (Editor's Note: This article is a WeChat web post. Suspected insiders have revealed the shady information of the CCP's biochemical weapon behind Wuhan Pneumonia Virus, and its content is more credible.)
The shocking secret behind Wuhan pneumonia
(All the text below comes from insiders who understand the inside of the CCP ’s research on viral weapons)
After the Gulf War, the Chinese Communist Party felt that there was a big gap between the United States and China in terms of national defense technology, so it stepped up its efforts to find asymmetric advantages in over-limit warfare, nuclear weapons, submarines, intelligence, and biochemical weapons.
In terms of biochemical weapons, the CCP has extensively studied chemical weapons, bacterial weapons, viral weapons, and genetic weapons. Several of them have been attacking viruses for many years, including two public P4 virus research institutes in China: Wuhan Institute of Virology, Chinese Academy of Sciences, and Harbin Veterinary Research Institute of Chinese Academy of Agricultural Sciences.
Interestingly, the Harbin Veterinary Research Institute and the base of the Japanese 731 Bacterial Troops are in the Harbin Pingfang District, only two or three kilometers away. The Chinese Communist Party inherited some of the equipment of the Japanese Army 's Avian Bacterial Troops, opened its own Bacterial Research Institute, and now focuses on virus research.
There are also several institutes directly under the PLA, including the Institute of Infectious Diseases at the PLA General Hospital. However, specialized weapon and virus research institutes usually have a team attached to the above-mentioned large institutions, and laboratories are often located in old forests in sparse mountains and sparsely populated places.
For a long time, the Chinese Communist Party has carefully studied smallpox virus, Ebola virus, HIV, Spanish flu virus, Hanta virus, rabies virus, SARS virus, MERS virus, Marburg virus, Mad Cow virus, Dengue virus and so on. Deadly virus information, the more poisonous the more interested.
SARS in 2003 showed them the terrible spread and lethality of the coronavirus. They then established a number of scientific research teams to vigorously attack the deadly coronavirus.
What needs to be explained here is that their main interest is not to study the cure of coronavirus, but how to improve the virus's virulence, how to hide it, and further expand the pathogenicity. Weaponization.
The main directions of virus weaponization are: first, to increase the virus's lethality, that is, lethality; second, to change the incubation period, that is, to be able to manipulate the incubation period of the virus, long or short; third, to infect the infectivity and infectivity of the incubation period; Sexuality means that it cannot be found to be an artificial virus and human-made transmission.
The Chinese Communist Party has repeatedly researched the types of deadly viruses in various virus research institutes and laboratories, which are transmitted between humans and animals, and from air, water, droplets, contact, and body fluids. Through the mutation of the virus in the host cell and the manipulation and assembly of artificial genes, we try to develop the ideal weapon-grade virus.
Weapon-grade viruses, once secret, spread undisclosed in enemy countries, ranging from a plague, a large-scale social chaos, and economic regression; on the other hand, a large number of people die, suffer injuries, and even destroy the country . And if it spreads in military camps, the consequences are unthinkable.
The harmfulness, concealment, and ease of use of this weapon greatly exceed nuclear and chemical weapons. It is an excellent asymmetric weapon that can enable weak countries to win huge asymmetric advantages in the face of strong countries.
The Communist Party of China studies virus weapons, and its main imaginary enemy is the United States. According to reports, during the most difficult period of the Sino-US trade war, the CCP considered the use of viral weapons to disrupt the United States.
People familiar with the matter said that some CCP generals had clamored that Ebola-class virus weapons were their new-generation nuclear weapons. "This thing is really a fortune of two or two, destroying a country in the invisible and effortlessly." "We want to have our own viper army!"
The CCP has never had the opportunity to apply viral weapons to enemy countries, but it has long been used to murder political opponents and important dissidents. In recent years, the suspicious deaths of political prisoners and dissidents have the shadow of biological weapons behind them.
While the U.S. military was eager to study the fixed-point removal of UAV missiles, the CCP agents took a different approach and invented a new word-"biochemical assassination." Prisons and detention centers are good places for human testing.
The P4 Virus Research Institute is the highest level of four-level protection. P4 = Protection 4, namely BSL 4, biosafety level 4. The main goal of Shi Zhengli's team is to develop weapon-grade coronaviruses. SARS and MERS viruses are her research materials.
There are two such laboratories open in China and less than 10 in Asia. Among them, experimental viruses and laboratory animals must be managed and controlled at the highest level.
However, due to chaotic management, it is not uncommon for Chinese virus research institutions to leak. It often happens that experimental animals flow into the people and even the market. Weapon-level virus leaks are no different from nuclear leaks, and they are even more harmful than nuclear leaks.
Wuhan Institute of Virology is located at 44 Xiaohongshan Central District, Wuchang District. Wuhan South China Seafood Market is located on Development Avenue in Jianghan District. The two are separated by a river, only 10 kilometers apart.
The cause of this pneumonia plague in Wuhan was precisely the coronavirus studied by the Shi Zhengli team of Wuhan Virus Research Institute. The outbreak was in the South China Seafood Market just across the river. Is it a coincidence? The problem is not so simple.
Weapons-grade viruses that were originally tailored for Americans, due to poor management, accidentally flowed into the seafood market through experimental animal snakes, harming hundreds of thousands of Chinese.
Can you say "Pick your own foot up again"?
Today, the Chinese Communist Party's army virus expert, Major General Chen Wei, is stationed in Wuhan and takes over the Wuhan Institute of Virology, which clearly proves the military background of the Institute.
Now, what they have to do is to control this accidental artificial plague, and the second is to keep secrets. The world must not be informed that Wuhan pneumonia was caused by the CCP’s leak of artificial virus weapons.
(Responsible editor: Yun Tao)
